Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:01.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:07.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:10.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:12.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
